How to run the application?

- npm install
- npm start   // for starting the application

BASEURL: http://localhost:5000/api
DOCUMENTATION_HOSTED_ON: http://localhost:5000/doc

// the application is tested using mocha and supertest
-npm test // for testing the application


// For API documentation
// swagger API documentation is used

// Api DOCUMENTAION IS HOSTED IN
URL-for-documentation: http://localhost:5000/doc



